Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我…救救这世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人得到魔神瑟列斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续旅程找寻余下的两部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在她们的目的地前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受命于神官谢加图的可怕敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正张牙舞爪等待她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的幻惑士卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们去了哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的打算打倒她们?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啊 收拾魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令你重回城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些水真干净呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找第二部魔神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 莫歌拿呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 它去了哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到 莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 那边好像有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是第二部魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 究竟要到哪里呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是上次那座岩山?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次被谢加图阻拦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你叫我们由这里前去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我们怎样去那里啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行的工具又被毁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会叫我们攀过\N那座峭壁吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我在河边洗了脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来又要弄得满身尘埃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 如果慢悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图的追兵就会赶到的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 令第二部魔神苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗没平坦的路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是浮在空中的岩山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特 我一定会收拾她们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心等我回来 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光为何总是那么有活力啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想生来就是热血少女呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!快来这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以前也在天空上看过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但锡菲罗真是\N一处美丽的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾美诺公主平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该一定更加 更加美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的锡菲罗\N是个怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么气味?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是花香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好晕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事!?\N地面突然…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次有岩石跌下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…\N难道又是魔物的所为吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…幻觉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻觉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚才好像被岩石击中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但完全不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跌下来的岩石完全不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这真的是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光! 小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地面也是幻觉吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知是幻觉还是站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是个山洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃进那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃进山洞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我的幻术会更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正可怕的现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摇晃不定的地面行走后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有晕车的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在阻挠我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们无法到达第二部魔神那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是谢加图的手下?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在这里也不可大意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会有什么出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了 传说的魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到吗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那声音是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你们很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何会在这种地方!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是被谢加图变成石头了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输给谢加图那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 艾美诺公主\N想和你们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主她…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被谢加图软禁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救了她出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫先生你…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说谎 最好的证据就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主想直接和你们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 公主殿下没事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有点古怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 的确是古列夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风你也看见吧 不会有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主在里面等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能这么轻易见到\N艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士啊 你们终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主 我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你知道谢加图弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你告诉我们 小风!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了得到魔神之外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他方法\N打倒谢加图了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你们死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主\N为何会变成魔物!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海\N一切全是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷阱!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N刚才的古列夫也…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错 恐怕是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍多少次也砍不完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是幻觉\N我们为何会受伤!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些伤痕或许也是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 痛楚是真实的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风 合上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才面对岩石和树时也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对这些魔物也一定奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 合上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划非常成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对我这个国色天香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身材玲珑浮凸的卡尔汀娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能活着回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我了结她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的岩石是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…干什么 莫歌拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我 收拾魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去收拾她们!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢伤害卡尔汀娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔兽召唤!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢伤害我的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!魔兽召唤!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好!不能消灭所有魔物!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!快醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉住那里的两位姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢伤害我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为回敬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要她们和我的朋友玩好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你真的令我生气了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然想伤害小光和小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你生气我也不会怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我的朋友!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!小风!没事吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来总算没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要攻击我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是谢加图的同党!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为谢加图说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果收拾了魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和朋友就可以一直住在城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上次问过他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他指那些魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子是我重要的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那些魔物也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是!你竟然…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然它们是那么重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何叫它们袭击我们!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们被杀死你也不在乎吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在乎啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N你为何要帮谢加图啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为大家讨厌我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去到哪里也不受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能在城堡一起生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友让大家感到麻烦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 我不命令它们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是绝对不会捣乱的呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要相信它们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你的朋友样子可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它们是好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你成为谢加图的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要它们做坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子\N就真的会变成坏孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你令这班孩子\N变成坏孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相识后也不是过了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们是珍贵的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁也会引以为荣\N的珍贵同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有同伴 我就能更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要为这些孩子想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能令它们得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有攻击你的朋友\N对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯阁特[葡萄名]!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿斯克特!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特\N肯和我们做朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定能成为好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特 怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收拾魔法骑士了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
